entries.s_494: I'm sorry. You aren't authorized to be here. I can't allow you access to the prisoner.
entries.s_496: Nice job. We'll go over the cell's holos and forward that intel to the higher-ups. You might already have one of these banners, but have another for your excellent work on Empire Day.
entries.s_498: I was watching on the monitors. He's a tough one. Anyway, I think it's best you leave before Vader returns.
entries.s_502: The Commander said I could take a look at the prisoner.
entries.s_504: Let's see...yes, you were added to the entry list. Better look now. I don't think that Jedi will last another session with Vader.
entries.s_506: Thanks for your help with interrogating the prisoner. There's not much more you can do at this point, leave the rest to Vader.
entries.s_508: I cannot allow anyone access without authorization from the Outpost Commander.
